about.summary: Provides convenience functions for advanced linear algebra with tensors and computation with datasets of tensors on a higher level abstraction. It includes Einstein and Riemann summing conventions, dragging, co- and contravariate indices, parallel computations on sequences of tensors.

name: r-tensora
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.36.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tensora
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tensorA_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tensorA/tensorA_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c7ffe12b99867675b5e9c9f31798f9521f14305c9d9f9485b171bcbd8697d09c

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1002
  skip: true  # [win32]
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tensorA')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tensorA')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://www.stat.boogaart.de/tensorA
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Provides convenience functions for advanced linear algebra with tensors and computation
    with datasets of tensors on a higher level abstraction. It includes Einstein and
    Riemann summing conventions, dragging, co- and contravariate indices, parallel computations
    on sequences of tensors.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - nick-youngblut
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
3.7.0
